data.description: Motivated Sellers. Charming home in the Ranches. Recently updated with brand new carpet, this West Jordan gem offers a refreshed and inviting interior. Plus, there's potential to expand your backyard oasis, perfect for customization to fit your lifestyle.  This 4-bed, 2.5-bath residence boasts modern amenities, a spacious layout, and a prime location. Immaculate interiors and a well-manicured yard make this property a must-see. Don't miss out on the chance to make this home uniquely yours! Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from county records.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
